Baby blues .. is a horror game made by KGames - Solo Indie Developer.  KGames is a independent game maker only worked on by one developer, Me known as Kumi (Official Channel is KumiOfficial. It was founded in 2011 as KumiGames (later changed to KGames) and Baby blues is my second officially released game.

This game takes place in a house, You play the role of Tommy the 3 year old kid living with his parents. While Tommy never experience anything in his life, this day will come when one day; He wakes up in the middle of the night, he steps off his bed and notice something is missing, his teddies. Tommy goes into the adventure where his only objective is to find his missing teddies and go back to bed, He doesn't care about anything else. While Searching for his teddies, Something strange is happening into the house but what is it?

Baby Blues V5: 
V5 will be one of the biggest updates to baby blues and will include all new scares, new horror, new sounds, new improved graphics, new effects, new features, new website and much much more.  The new version of Baby blues will be far scarier then the older versions, and will be updated to a more scary experience for all the players! Do you have what it takes to find them now? You can donate any amount to get the faster early release for Baby Blues V5.
